\pard\f0\fs28 Subgen.{\b  Lotoidea} Pers. Flowers subtended by free or united bracts (or short glandular hairs). Calyx-throat open, without a ring of hairs or a callosity. Legume included in the calyx or exserted. Seeds (1-)2-4(-10).
